  "detailed_description": "<h1>TRADING CARDS!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190110/extras/977372e310e2b84fcb8bc4b2c0e986f4.avif?t=1581628957\" width=580 height=270 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HENTAI SNIPER: Middle East</h2>In this first-person sniper shooter our special H.E.N.T.A.I. Agent has received the most dangerous and difficult task possible: clear out the ruins of once city from terrorists.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190110/extras/3283a92581e3f6fda9ccb6531d9b4c31.poster.avif?t=1581628957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190110/extras/3283a92581e3f6fda9ccb6531d9b4c31.webm?t=1581628957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190110/extras/3283a92581e3f6fda9ccb6531d9b4c31.mp4?t=1581628957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2>There is nothing left of what was once a city. Nowadays it is an abandoned, heavily guarded by terrorists territory. Not once before we were able to come this close to their base. This is our best chance to fight them back.. for the H.E.N.T.A.I.!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shooting game based on sniper mechanics<br></li><li>User-friendly and simple controls<br></li><li>A variety of satisfying animations</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlist the game and be the first one to win the terrorists over!</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HENTAI SNIPER: Middle East</h2>In this first-person sniper shooter our special H.E.N.T.A.I. Agent has received the most dangerous and difficult task possible: clear out the ruins of once city from terrorists.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190110/extras/3283a92581e3f6fda9ccb6531d9b4c31.poster.avif?t=1581628957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190110/extras/3283a92581e3f6fda9ccb6531d9b4c31.webm?t=1581628957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190110/extras/3283a92581e3f6fda9ccb6531d9b4c31.mp4?t=1581628957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2>There is nothing left of what was once a city. Nowadays it is an abandoned, heavily guarded by terrorists territory. Not once before we were able to come this close to their base. This is our best chance to fight them back.. for the H.E.N.T.A.I.!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shooting game based on sniper mechanics<br></li><li>User-friendly and simple controls<br></li><li>A variety of satisfying animations</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlist the game and be the first one to win the terrorists over!</h2>",
